videos.description:
Hidden Agenda - Full Game Gameplay Walkthrough (With Good / Best Ending)

Hidden Agenda is a new crime thriller from Supermassive Games and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment.

The story follows the hunt for the infamous "Trapper" killer. You play as two different characters throughout the story, Becky who is a detective and Felicity, who is a district attorney. The game is unique in the sense that it's a movie, but incorporates gameplay elements into it. This video is a full walkthrough of the game, with the good/best ending, no unnecessary commentary and on the PS4 Pro.

You will also not be using the regular PS4 controller to play this game, it's all done through PlayLink. PlayLink is a new way for family & friends to play games together together, as it uses smartphones and tablets as controllers.
videos.author: HarryNinetyFour
videos.title: Hidden Agenda - Full Game Gameplay Walkthrough (With Good / Best Ending)
